tetrominos
------------------------------------------
Simple Tetris game written in C++ with ncurses lib.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-2.9.0-3
  libgcc1-6.4.0-1
  libncursesw10-6.0-11.20170617
  libstdc++6-6.4.0-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.28-3
  cygport-0.24.1-1
  gcc-core-6.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-6.4.0-1
  make-4.2.1-2

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/sparkoo/NTetris

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/sparkoo/NTetris/archive/1.0.1.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack tetrominos-1.0.1-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./tetrominos-1.0.1-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/tetrominos-1.0.1-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/tetrominos-1.0.1-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(tetrominos)
  /usr/bin/ntetris.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/tetrominos.README
  /usr/share/doc/tetrominos/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/tetrominos/README.md

------------------

